<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Bethlehema Naupieng</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chanchin deihum Angelte thu ngai un,
 A pahchaknau gi chun van a thawng a;
 Leia Lalpen thak hung pieng chu chawian un,
 Lawpna, Kipahna a hung luong let tai.

[V2]
 Aw Bethlehem nau pieng chawian un,
 Nam tin, chi tinin Amah lawp uh hen;
 Tuhin lawp takin chwian hitiu,
 'Lalpa lopi, Halleluijah ti'n.

[V3]
 2. Van aksi lopi'n lam a salhvaka,
 Suohlam michingte chiehna ma a pui;
 Lawp takin a maa khunin a ho ui,
 Chamna Lal a pieng, lungkham bei ina.

[V4]
 3. Aw hun kipahum ah chawian hitiu,
 La san chawian hitiu gi hawih cheng tawh;
 I aw neihsun chengun chawihat la sai tiu,
 Vakna a tung tai thimna bei tan a.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>19</hymn_number>
</song>